# Typeahead onItemSelect â€“ Event-Driven Sibling Field Population

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Event Type

#### [MODIFY] [form-component-event.types.ts](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/form-state/events/form-component-event.types.ts)

```ts
export interface FieldItemSelectedEvent extends FieldScopedEventBase {
    readonly type: 'field.item.selected';
    readonly selectedItem: unknown | null;
}
```

Add `FIELD_ITEM_SELECTED` constant, map entry, union member, and `createFieldItemSelectedEvent` factory.

