### 4. `onItemSelect` Config Type

#### [MODIFY] [field-component.outline.ts](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/packages/sails-ng-common/src/config/field-component.outline.ts)

Add to [FieldComponentConfigFrame](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/packages/sails-ng-common/src/config/field-component.outline.ts#8-10):

```ts
onItemSelect?: {
    /** Dot-path into selectedItem.raw (or selectedItem) to extract this field's value */
    rawPath: string;
    /**
     * Value to set when selection is cleared. Defaults to null.
     * Should be type-compatible with the target control (e.g. string for text inputs, null for optional fields).
     */
    clearValue?: unknown;
    /**
     * Future: optional source constraint (e.g. sourceField pointer) to scope consumption
     * when multiple producer typeaheads can exist under one parent container.
     * Not implemented in initial version.
     */
    // sourceField?: string;
};
```

