### 5. Wrapper Integration

#### [MODIFY] [base-wrapper.component.ts](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/component/base-wrapper.component.ts)

- Add `FormComponentItemSelectEventProducer` + `FormComponentItemSelectEventConsumer`.
- Add **optional** `injector?` to [FormComponentEventBindingOptions](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/form-state/events/form-component-base-event-producer-consumer.ts#14-20) (in [form-component-base-event-producer-consumer.ts](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/form-state/events/form-component-base-event-producer-consumer.ts)) â€” optional ensures backward compatibility with existing producer/consumer call sites. Pass `inject(Injector)` from wrapper only for the item select producer.
- Producer gated by `shouldAttachItemSelectProducer()`: checks `component.selectedItem` signal exists.
- Consumer gated by `shouldAttachItemSelectConsumer()`: checks `onItemSelect` config present.
- Destroy both in [ngOnDestroy()](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/component/base-wrapper.component.ts#148-157).

