#### [MODIFY] [typeahead-input.component.ts](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/component/typeahead-input.component.ts)

- Add: `public readonly selectedItem = signal<TypeaheadOption | null>(null)`
- In [onSelect()](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/component/typeahead-input.component.ts#167-181) after [setModelFromOption()](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/component/typeahead-input.component.ts#332-343): `this.selectedItem.set(selected)`
- **Stale selection invalidation**: In `displayControl.valueChanges` subscription, when user manually edits the display text and `selectedItem()` is non-null: `this.selectedItem.set(null)`. **Gated by `programmaticDisplayUpdate` flag** â€” only invalidates on user-initiated edits, not programmatic label writes after [onSelect()](file:///Users/shilo/Work/Projects/redbox/redbox-portal/feature/typeahead-onitemselect/angular/projects/researchdatabox/form/src/app/component/typeahead-input.component.ts#167-181).

